Name: DivKis01
AboutMe: Divick Kishore is an entrepreneur and technology freak. An alumnus of IIT Kanpur, he has Co-Founded iWish Inc. and Co-Founded and Architected, GreenLoader, an uber downloader and NAS device for low power consumption. He has versatile experience ranging from Embedded Systems to Parallel Processing Systems; Hands-on platforms as diverse as graphics device drivers to Web2.0 websites / apps. He has worked for some of the most respected tech companies in the world like ARM and Silicon Graphics. He loves watching and playing football(soccer) and badminton.
